What is socially &amp; morally accepted &quot;still&quot; in our day &amp; age.<br>
<br>
Not saying either is good or bad for anybody but being in the criminal justice field for over 10yrs now I have seen the effects of what both end in.<br>
<br>
On one hand..<br>
Have seen more damage inflicted resulting from alcohol use/abuse in our community, city and nearby reservations.<br>
<br>
On the other hand..<br>
Have seen &quot;weed&quot; as causing more underlining factors which in its form is also a serious harm mirroring alcohol use/abuse.<br>
<br>
Dont know what the answer trully could be for society as a whole.. but I do foresee it being legalized in the next 10yrs.<br>
